{"tid":1807364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（保命求推）香港人正式全民戴口罩","createTime":"2020-01-01T18:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T11:06:17.000Z","uid":125168,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"58ac1905ad4f91a43c8fbd61e7855f1cd4796243","tid":1807364,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbHPvKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbHPvKY.jpg&h=0d48473d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請回想起當年沙士 都係廣東爆發再傳染落黎香港 <br />\n<br />\n之後俾個19正苦掩住單野 <br />\n結果全港社區再爆發<br />\n<br />\n肺炎不論咩種  本身傳染力就好高<br />\n本channel在此高度重視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果都係大陸既事再惹落香港"},{"pid":"73b2176ad9f2e73661e048d1e898fdcedbe630f8","tid":1807364,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"❗⚠️高危 嚴重警告⚠️❗️未fc<br />\n<br />\n請小心本港再次爆發肺炎疾病<br />\n<br />\n❕屯門醫院有一單武漢人肺炎求疹個案<br />\n❗️已咳出血並高燒<br />\n<br />\n請由聽日開始全面防範高傳染性肺炎<br />\n<br />\n特別係進出過醫院既人 <br />\n<br />\n⚠️全日口罩<br />\n⚠️勤洗手<br />\n⚠️做好個人衛生<br />\n<br />\n唔想你身邊既人 <br />\n手足或者自己中招就要至少做好以上三樣"},{"pid":"dcfa4dcb362ac172ebbf5ea9d3273f57243192ae","tid":1807364,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"幫推行動，同身邊人宣傳，戴個口罩無成本, 但係中咗招死埋就一世"},{"pid":"5bdd47181acd92c16805cea5da77af24ee4a8f93","tid":1807364,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a2eb62b73e0dfa062fe18fdc3389658c5837b3","tid":1807364,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1d9ad08ffdfe73e3ad47b0d87703af7d1f0fcaea","tid":1807364,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223f77a054c6d875b79208